  <official_title>A Multi-Center, Randomized, Double-Blind, Placebo-Controlled, Crossover Study in Women With Irritable Bowel Syndrome to Evaluate Feasibility and Reproducibility of Barostat Assessments of Colorectal Sensation During Colorectal Distention and Its Pharmacological Modulation Using Octreotide.</official_title>
